photometry.remarks: The Apparent Magnitude was calculated with APT by Melina Thévenot, using a reference star in Pan-STARRS (http://vizier.u-strasbg.fr/viz-bin/VizieR-5?-ref=VIZ5cd939042595&-out.add=.&-source=II/349/ps1&-c=131.116761890%20%2b18.265797100,eq=J2000,rs=2&-out.orig=o) an Absolute Magnitude of -15.23 was also calculated.

The Apparent Magnitude was calculated with APT by Melina Thévenot, using a reference star in Pan-STARRS (http://vizier.u-strasbg.fr/viz-bin/VizieR-5?-ref=VIZ5cd939042595&-out.add=.&-source=II/349/ps1&-c=131.116761890%20%2b18.265797100,eq=J2000,rs=2&-out.orig=o) an Absolute Magnitude of -14.72 was also calculated.
